activities: DNAnexus provides a platform for managing, analyzing, and sharing genomic information.  Users may upload personal information into their DNAnexus accounts.
eucountries: Austria, Belgium, Bulgaria, Cyprus, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, France, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Iceland, Ireland, Italy, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Malta, Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Romania, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, United Kingdom
personaldata: DNAnexus users may upload organization, client, customer, and/or clinical trial data to their account.  DNAnexus does not manually process any customer data.
recoursemech: DNAnexus has engaged BBB EU Safe Harbor to provide a private sector dispute resolution mechanism.
